                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p><hi rend=\"underline\">$40 Enclosed</hi>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>202 St. Paul Street</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Montreal</placeName>\n                <date>Aug. 24th/54</date>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>    <placeName>Phila.</placeName></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dear Sir.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">I returned<lb/> from <placeName>New York</placeName> on\n                    <date>Monday</date> and<lb/> found your note of <date>3d</date> inst. with<lb/>\n                an enclosed for <persName>Mr. De Sola</persName>, which<lb/> was delivered. Accept\n                my heart-<lb/>felt thanks for your kindness.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I leave another favour to ask of<lb/> you, which I am confident you\n                will<lb/> kindly execute for me. While<lb/> a Prisoner at\n                    <placeName>Wilmington</placeName> I had<lb/> occasion to borrow some money<lb/>\n                on a <hi rend=\"underline\">diamond ring</hi> from a <persName><hi rend=\"underline\"\n                        >Mr</hi>.<lb/>\n                    <hi rend=\"underline\">Raw</hi></persName>, who keeps a clothing store<lb/> in\n                    <placeName>Wilmington</placeName> on <placeName>Market Street near<lb/> 4<hi\n                        rend=\"sup\">th</hi></placeName>. He loaned me $20, for which<lb/> I promised\n                to pay him $23. He<lb/> gave me a receipt for the ring, which<lb/> I forwarded to\n                    <persName>Mr. Frankel</persName>. <persName>Mr. F.</persName><lb/> has promised\n                to get me the ring, ac-<lb/>cording to the enclosed letter. I also<lb/> owe\n                    <persName>Mr. Frankel</persName> $15 which he kind-<lb/>ly loaned me. I\n                therefore enclose</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3rf5m211/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
